This Invitation to Tender (the “ITT”) is an invitation by the City of Camrose (“the City”) to prospective bidders to submit bids for 2026 Underground Construction Program – 51 Avenue and 52 Street, as further described in Section A of the ITT Particulars (Appendix A) (the “Deliverables”). 

The work in this Invitation to Tender includes, but is not limited to, the following: 

a. Asphalt sawcutting;
b. Asphalt removals;
